SmartPoi Connections:

esp8266:
1. RXD - not connected
2. GPIO 0 - to APA102 Clock In
3. GPIO 2 - via R1 to APA102 Data In
4. GND - ground
5. TXD - not connected
6. CH_PD pulled high via R2
7. RST - pulled high via R3
8. VCC - to 3.3v

new dimensions with header: height 16mm width27mm length37mm

AfroCard dimensions from C-Boards: width 140mm height 180mm



